282
00:21:34,679 --> 00:21:37,279
That lady just likes to worry about people.

283
00:21:38,994 --> 00:21:40,794
Tell me.

284
00:21:40,794 --> 00:21:44,061
In the afternoon, was something bothering you?

285
00:21:47,520 --> 00:21:51,670
