293
00:22:13,920 --> 00:22:17,200
One time, your grandpa was sick and almost didn't make it.

294
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:20,040
We couldn't contact him no matter how hard we tried.

295
00:22:20,040 --> 00:22:23,400
Back then, communications weren't as advanced as it is now.

296
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:25,799
Later on, we were finally able to save your grandpa.

297
00:22:25,799 --> 00:22:28,699
We got into contact with your uncle. We wanted him to come home,

298
00:22:28,699 --> 00:22:32,759
but he spoke haltingly for a while and said that he couldn't.

299
00:22:32,759 --> 00:22:36,340
He said that since your grandpa was fine now, his current mission was also very important.

300
00:22:36,340 --> 00:22:39,320
He could only come home after completing his mission.

301
00:22:39,320 --> 00:22:42,419
And he ended up coming home only after one month.

302
00:22:42,419 --> 00:22:45,900
All of us siblings were mad at him and treated him coldly.

303
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:49,634
Back then, your grandaunt came to visit,

304
00:22:49,634 --> 00:22:52,980
and pointed at him and scolded him for being unfilial.

305
00:22:52,980 --> 00:22:57,100
Your uncle just listened and didn't say a word.

306
00:22:57,100 --> 00:22:58,440
You were still so little back then.

307
00:22:58,440 --> 00:23:04,400
You suddenly said, "Grandaunt, isn't your son working in the USA?"

308
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:06,540
Your grandaunt loved hearing that the most.

309
00:23:06,540 --> 00:23:11,839
She said, "Right. Yu Tu, study hard too, and go to the USA in the future."

310
00:23:11,839 --> 00:23:17,320
Then you said, "Grandaunt, your son hasn't visited you for so many years.

311
00:23:17,320 --> 00:23:19,820
Why don't you scold him for being unfilial?"

312
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:24,179
Back then, I thought,

313
00:23:24,179 --> 00:23:27,300
they both can't be with their parents.

314
00:23:27,300 --> 00:23:29,680
If you live abroad, people envy you.

315
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:31,840
If you're in the northwest of China, and silently making your contribution,

316
00:23:31,840 --> 00:23:34,540
people would say that it's not worth it, and even consider you unfilial.

317
00:23:34,540 --> 00:23:36,381
Does that make sense?

318
00:23:36,381 --> 00:23:38,680
All of us adults couldn't figure it out.

319
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:41,960
We were no better than a ten-year-old child like you.

320
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:43,760
I've been smart since I was little.

321
00:23:43,760 --> 00:23:47,240
Of course. You're my son.

322
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:50,740
Son.

323
00:23:50,740 --> 00:23:53,580
You know about the truths of life.

324
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:56,920
But when it comes to yourself, you're confused.

325
00:23:58,360 --> 00:24:01,896
Actually, the thing I regret the most in my life

326
00:24:01,896 --> 00:24:07,156
