327
00:24:07,156 --> 00:24:09,340
What was I thinking back then?

328
00:24:09,340 --> 00:24:13,920
I thought, "My son has such high grades. He must go into the most popular major.

329
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:16,360
Otherwise, his grades would be wasted."

330
00:24:17,360 --> 00:24:22,020
Later on, I found out that you secretly studied two majors.

331
00:24:22,020 --> 00:24:24,360
I regretted it so much.

332
